pan class=\"tc\">(Trad.: 譏)</span></div><b>Chinese Definition:</b>\n      <div><b>Pictophonetic</b>: <span class=\"semantic\"><a class=\"dictips\">几</a></span> indicates the sound; <span class=\"phonetic\"><a class=\"dictips\">讠</a></span> (speech) conveys the meaning.</div>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n</div>\n<div id=\"purpleculture_tree\">\n  <div class=\"tree\">\n    <ul>\n      <li><span class=\"str_def\">⿰</span> <span class=\"str_desc\">Left to right</span>\n        <ul>\n          <li><span class=\"str_def\"><a class=\"dictips\">讠</a></span> <span class=\"str_py\">[ <a href=\"allsetlearning-yan2.mp3\" class=\"pinyin tone2\">yán</a> ]</span> <span class=\"str_desc\">words, speech; to speak, to say</span></li>\n          <li><span class=\"str_def\"><a class=\"dictips\">几</a></span> <span class=\"str_py\">[ <a href=\"allsetlearning-ji3.mp3\" class=\"pinyin tone3\">jǐ</a> ]</span> <span class=\"str_desc\">small table; how many; a few, some</span></li>\n        </ul>\n      </li>\n    </ul>\n  </div>\n</div>\n<hr><span id=\"purpleculture_examples\">①讽刺，挖苦：讥讽。讥评。讥笑。讥诮。冷讥热嘲。<br>②查问，察问。<br>③指责，非议：讥议。讥弹(tán)(指责，抨击)。<br>④规劝。<br><a href=\"https://www.purpleculture.net/dictionary-details?word=%E8%AE%A5%E8%AE%BD\" class=\"sword\">讥讽</a> [ <a href=\"allsetlearning-ji1.mp3\" class=\"pinyin tone1\">jī</a> <a href=\"allsetlearning-feng3.mp3\" class=\"pinyin tone3\">fěng</a> ]: to satirize; to ridicule; to mock<br><a href=\"https://www.purpleculture.net/dictionary-details?word=%E8%AE%A5%E7%AC%91\" class=\"sword\">讥笑</a> [ <a href=\"allsetlearning-ji1.mp3\" class=\"pinyin tone1\">jī</a> <a href=\"allsetlearning-xiao4.mp3\" class=\"pinyin tone4\">xiào</a> ]: to sneer<br><a href=\"https://www.purpleculture.net/dictionary-details?word=%E8%AE%A5%E5%88%BA\" class=\"sword\">讥刺</a> [ <a href=\"allsetlearning-ji1.mp3\" class=\"pinyin tone1\">jī</a> <a href=\"allsetlearning-ci4.mp3\" class=\"pinyin tone4\">cì</a> ]: to ridicule; to mock<br><a href=\"https://www.purpleculture.net/dictionary-details?word=%E8%AE%A5%E8%AF%AE\" class=\"sword\">讥诮</a> [ <a href=\"allsetlearning-ji1.mp3\" class=\"pinyin tone1\">jī</a> <a href=\"allsetlearning-qiao4.mp3\" class=\"pinyin tone4\">qiào</a> ]: to deride; to mock</span>\n<hr>\n<div>\n  <div>\n    <div><span class=\"tc\">(Trad.: 譏)</span></div><b>Chinese Definition:</b>\n    <div><b>Pictophonetic</b>: <span class=\"semantic\"><a class=\"dictips\">几</a></span> indicates the sound; <span class=\"phonetic\"><a class=\"dictips\">讠</a></span> (speech) conveys the meaning.</div>\n  </div>\n</div>\n<div>HSK: 6</div>\n<div>Freq: 2922</div>\n<div><span style=\"color:tomato\">Chinese</span>: When a politicians words sound like a bunch of hot wind he always gets derided by the opposing party.</div>\n<hr>\n<div><span style=\"color:#f5950f\">Meaning:</span> deride<br><span style=\"color:#f5950f\">Hanzi:</span> 譏<br><span style=\"color:#f5950f\">Story:</span> It was useful in the past but the abacus isn't very helpful for saying how many anymore so some people deride (ridicule) it with their words and mention it's modern replacements.<br><span style=\"color:#f5950f\">Kind:</span> simplified<br><img src=\"35663.gif\"></div>\n<div>\n  <hr>\n</div>\n<div id=\"hanziyuan\">\n  <div class=\"etymology-nav\" id=\"&#x8BA5;\">\n    <div class=\"alert alert-success etymology-alert m-0\" role=\"alert\"></div>\n    <div class=\"row bg-info border-purple border-top mx-0 row-eq-height\" id=\"E02525\">\n      <div class=\"col-md-3 col-sm-4 p-0\">\n        <div class=\"p-1\">\n          <p></p>\n          <p><b>Traditional in your browser 繁体字的浏览器显示:</b><span class=\"text-lg\">&#x8B4F;</span></p>\n          <p><b>Traditional in Unicode standard 繁体字的Unicode标准:</b><a href=\"https://www.unicode.org/cgi-bin/GetUnihanData.pl?codepoint=8B4F\" target=\"_blank\">U+8B4F</a><img src=\"https://www.unicode.org/cgi-bin/refglyph?24-8B4F\"></p>\n          <p><b>Older traditional characters 旧繁体字/异体字:</b> Not exist</p>\n          <p><b>Simplified in your browser 简